# {{NAME}} — knowledge-context pack

{{DESCRIPTION}}

A Spaces pack (`{{PACK_ID}}`, tile `{{COMPONENT}}`) that indexes this Space into a
portable OKF (`okf-ext/{{OKF_VERSION}}`) bundle, built with `okf-pack`.

## Use

- The host mounts this pack and runs `okf-pack serve --rpc stdio`.
- Indexing and querying require an embedder; this Space is configured for
  `{{EMBEDDER}}` (net mode `{{NET_MODE}}`). Set it in `.okf/config.toml`.
- To mount in a Space, merge `.space/manifest.patch.toml` into the Space manifest.

